[SHORT DESC]
If hit by a special attack, returns double the damage.

[LONG DESC]
<p>If the last special attack to hit the user was from an opposing Pokémon, this attack deals double the damage done to that Pokémon. Does not affect Dark-type Pokémon, but hits everything else for the same damage.</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/dp/moves/metal_burst">Metal Burst</a> is a Steel-type equivalent, but affects both physical and special moves.<br/ >
<a href="/dp/moves/counter">Counter</a> is a Fighting-type equivalent, but affects physical attacks instead of special.</p>